1) Download Node Exporter using CMD
   wget https://github.com/prometheus/node_exporter/releases/download/v1.8.0/node_exporter-1.8.0.linux-386.tar.gz

2) Extract  using CMD
   tar -xzf node_exporter-1.8.0.linux-386.tar.gz

3) Move Node Exporter to below location
   sudo mv node_exporter /usr/local/bin/node_exporter

4) Create Service file for auto start
